{"tid":2371002,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府再批27.9億助海洋公園「填氹」 54億還款期延至2059年 免收利息","createTime":"2021-01-18T12:38:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T07:51:22.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"5f3c8679ff613dcf81da81982df4386d8c18413b","tid":2371002,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T12:38:46.000Z","msg":"政府早前向公園撥款54億元救亡，今日當局再宣佈撥16.7億填氹，另提供11.2億助公園推廣保育教育；而早前港府就海洋公園發展計劃及大樹灣水上樂園工程的貸款餘額（共54億元），還款期亦獲延至2059年，而且更免收利息，以支援轉型。政府文件顯示，新建議的貸款安排將使政府收入減少約40億元。<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華今午公佈，海洋公園將轉型成為全新的零售、餐飲、消閒的中心，山下免費入場，但山上就逐項設施收費，更允許公園外判大部份保育以外的設施以減省開支，期望各項改革完成後，公園可達至自負營虧。他稱，為支援公園改建及轉型，當局會向海洋公園提供一系列資金支援。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210118/KGHBCHKRRZC7RNGWJACFANWNOA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210118%2FKGHBCHKRRZC7RNGWJACFANWNOA%2F&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrOgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=1b282d95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210118%2FKGHBCHKRRZC7RNGWJACFANWNOA%2F&h=24c1a53b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210118/KGHBCHKRRZC7RNGWJACFANWNOA/</a>"},{"pid":"5a6352aaec1d8971e78f78effeba131b707db3e2","tid":2371002,"uid":331421,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T12:40:02.000Z","msg":"8年後先開始還錢，供樓都無啲咁荀既plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3400917eccdf7788a6c25ff53a0615cfcb07595","tid":2371002,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a6352aaec1d8971e78f78effeba131b707db3e2","tid":2371002,"uid":331421,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T12:40:02.000Z","msg":"8年後先開始還錢，供樓都無啲咁荀既plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T12:40:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face